    # dissolve
    regions = mexico_estados[[cluster_type, "geometry"]].to_crs(6362).dissolve(by=cluster_type)
    #sacar el ipq
    ipqs = shapestats.isoperimetric_quotient(regions)
    #DF
    result = {cluster_type:ipqs}
    results.update(result)

fit_scores = []
